content: How much do I owe in taxes?

Tax rate,Taxable income threshold
3.35%, on the portion of taxable income that is $47900 or less, plus
6.60%, on the portion of taxable income over $47900 up to $116000 plus
7.60%, on the portion of taxable income over $116000 up to $242000 plus
8.75%, on the portion of taxable income over $242000
